metadata.name: Clearing the Fog of Mind
metadata.description:
Fog and clouds envelop us as we rise above Wall Street. The iconic golden bull stands ready to charge right at the entrance of the building we chose. Every step takes us away from that world and into our own, one where we belong. We are here to do our work, the very thing that gives us freedom away from the shackles of the financial institutions we rise above. The ethereal fog is an epiphany for my soul reminding me I am, exactly   where    I need  to be.                 I create therefor I am.

Photo created during a foggy morning above the Bull of Wall Street. Lil Mahnaji as photographed by EM1T.
